    "body" : "<p>I am using Idea 8.\nin your module dependancies tab (in the project structure dialog).  Add a \"Module Library\".  There you can select a Jar Directory to add.  Then make sure the run profile is using the Classpath and JDK of the correct module when it runs (this is in the run config dialog.</p>\n"
