    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1560201478,
    "creation_date" : 1560201478,
    "answer_id" : 56533662,
    "question_id" : 854264,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need not specify the classes folder. Intellij should be able to load it.\nYou will get this error if \"Project Compiler output\" is blank.</p>\n\n<p>Just make sure that below value is set:\n<strong>Project Settings -> Project -> Project Compiler output</strong> \nto your <strong><em>projectDir/out</em></strong> folder</p>\n"
  }, {
